title: cAdvisor Pods/Containers: CPU Utilisation
agents: prometheus
catalog: containerization/cadvisor
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:

 This check measures the CPU utilisation of containers and/or pods.

 This check obtains its metrics values through Prometheus. In order to allow
 generation of cAdvisor related CPU services, the user needs to enable
 the cAdvisor option under the Prometheus Datasource Programs ruleset.

inventory:
 One service is created for each CPU.
